===Noun===
'''Deej'''

#(''derogatory slang'') A child with [[special needs]]; by extension, a person of low intelligence or having the appearance of a person with special needs.
# Someone who is deemed to be a failure by their peers.
# Used in similar manner to the Scots word [[glaikit]].